data.description: *SELLER MOTIVATED!!!*SELLER WILL ASSISTANCE WITH CLOSING COSTS!!!Welcome to this two-story 3648 sqft home nestled away ready for a new owner to make it their own! The home features a brand-new roof, an office space, a modern granite kitchen, water softener, large bonus space, solar panels, and an outdoor kitchen with an enclosed pool and deck. Behind the screen is an open green backyard that consists of avocado trees, lemon trees and mangos trees with plenty of more space to improve your green thumb. Welcome to peace and quiet when joining the Crystal Cove Resort community that is not too far away from Disney, Universal, SeaWorld, shopping, dining, and other adventure filled activities. The community has a clubhouse, pool, gym and playground. HOA services lawn care, grounds maintenance, garbage and recycling. This home also has an opportunity to become an air bnb that can make this home an income producing investment. With a little bit of personal touch, this home can be perfect for personal use, business use or even both! Come take a tour and see what opportunity awaits you!
